sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as vLLM Orchestrator Gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-detector)
    participant LLM as vLLM / LLM Server

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer Token (pass-through)<br/>{"stream": false, "messages": [...]}
    Note over Gateway: Inject route's detector config<br/>(input/output detector maps)<br/>into request payload
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization header forwarded<br/>Optional mTLS client cert<br/>{"detectors": {input: [...], output: [...]}, ...}
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run configured detectors<br/>(content analysis)
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>LLM: Generate completion
    LLM-->>Orchestrator: Generated text
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: Response with detection metadata<br/>{"choices": [...], "detections": {...}}
    Note over Gateway: If detections found AND<br/>fallback_message configured:<br/>replace choices[0].message.content
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>(original or fallback message)

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Detection (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer Token (pass-through)<br/>{"stream": true, "messages": [...]}
    Note over Gateway: Inject route's detector config<br/>into request payload
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization header forwarded<br/>Optional mTLS client cert<br/>{"stream": true, "detectors": {...}, ...}
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run configured detectors
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>LLM: Generate completion (streaming)

    loop SSE Chunks
        LLM-->>Orchestrator: Chunk
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE data: {chunk + detection metadata}
        Note over Gateway: Parse SSE line, strip "data: " prefix<br/>Check for detections<br/>Apply fallback on first detected chunk
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE data: {chunk}<br/>(original or fallback)
    end

    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE data: [DONE]
    Note over Gateway: Filter [DONE] sentinel
    Gateway-->>Client: SSE data: [DONE]
